abstract: >
  ATLAS is a Docker-based machine learning and data science
  environment optimized for NVIDIA RTX 4060 Laptop GPU with
  16GB RAM. It provides a tiered build system supporting core
  data science (base), LLM inference (llm), and LLM acceleration
  (full) configurations, with optional materials science support.
